Package: MoPAC
Type: Package
Title: Modular Pipeline for the Analysis of CRISPR screens
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Oscar D Villarreal and Han Xu
Maintainer: Oscar D Villarreal <oscardvillarreal@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Description: The Modular Pipeline for the Analysis of CRISPR screens generates unbiased essentiality and differential essentiality gene scores from FASTQ files of high-throughput functional pooled screens as well as from either raw or normalized tables of read counts.
